node.text:
Did somebody say vegan Thai food? 😍
This meal was heavenly. The flavours, the colours, the textures. 
It sure was a wow moment! 

This was at @gigglingsquid and on first impressions I would give it an 8/10. The service let it down, as the servers tried to give us chicken wings and after telling them no, all of our dishes should be vegan, they proceeded to ask us if the squid was ours 🥴 

Once we had our correct dishes though, it was thoroughly enjoyable! 

I opted for (most of🤣) the vegan tapas options including 
▫️Mushroom larb 
▫️Spring rolls
▫️Ruby noodle with bean sprouts
▫️Pak Choi and tenderstems 
▫️Sticky Rice 
and we also had the chilli and basil gra pao stir fry 🌱🤍
